R. J. COATS, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6057. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 5, 1930.

Before RUDKIN and WILBUR, Circuit Judges and KERRIGAN, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed.
